<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LanguageData>
    <!-- RimMindAdvisorMod.cs -->

    <!-- Settings -->
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.Tab>顾问</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.Tab>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableAdvisor>启用 AI 顾问系统</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableAdvisor>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableAdvisor.Desc>开启后，AI 会根据殖民者的状态和性格为其选择下一步行动。</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableAdvisor.Desc>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.ShowThoughtBubble>显示 AI 决策气泡</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.ShowThoughtBubble>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.ShowThoughtBubble.Desc>在殖民者头顶显示 AI 选择该行动的理由。</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.ShowThoughtBubble.Desc>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.CustomPrompt>自定义系统提示词（注入到上下文之前）</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.CustomPrompt>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.TriggerSources>触发来源</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.TriggerSources>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableIdleTrigger>小人空闲时触发</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableIdleTrigger>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableIdleTrigger.Desc>当殖民者没有工作时，AI 主动为其选择下一步行动。</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableIdleTrigger.Desc>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableMoodTrigger>心情低于阈值时触发</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableMoodTrigger>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableMoodTrigger.Desc>当殖民者心情过低时，AI 优先为其选择能改善心情的行动。</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableMoodTrigger.Desc>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.PawnScanInterval>小人扫描间隔：{0} ticks（约{1}s）</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.PawnScanInterval>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.PawnScanInterval.Desc>扫描空闲小人的频率。越小越灵敏，但性能开销越高。</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.PawnScanInterval.Desc>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.MoodThreshold>心情触发阈值：{0}%</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.MoodThreshold>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.MoodThreshold.Desc>殖民者心情低于此百分比时触发 AI 顾问。</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.MoodThreshold.Desc>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.RequestCooldown>请求冷却：{0} 游戏小时（{1} ticks）</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.RequestCooldown>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.RequestCooldown.Desc>同一殖民者两次 AI 请求之间的最短间隔。</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.RequestCooldown.Desc>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.MaxConcurrent>最大并发请求数：{0}</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.MaxConcurrent>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.MaxConcurrent.Desc>同时向 AI 发送请求的上限。增大可提高响应速度，但会增加 API 费用。</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.MaxConcurrent.Desc>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.Section.Display>显示</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.Section.Display>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.Section.Request>请求设置</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.Section.Request>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.RequestExpire>审批请求过期：{0} 游戏天</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.RequestExpire>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.RequestExpire.Desc>审批悬浮窗的过期时间。超过此时间未响应的审批请求将自动关闭。</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.RequestExpire.Desc>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.NoTriggerWarning>警告：无触发源已启用，AI 顾问不会自动激活。</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.NoTriggerWarning>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.RiskWithoutApprovalWarning>警告：审批系统已关闭，风险拦截将不生效，所有动作直接执行。</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.RiskWithoutApprovalWarning>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.Section.Approval>审批与拦截</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.Section.Approval>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableRequestSystem>启用请求系统（殖民者主动请求需玩家批准）</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableRequestSystem>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableRequestSystem.Desc>开启后，殖民者可以主动向玩家提出行动请求，需批准后才执行。</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableRequestSystem.Desc>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableRiskApproval>启用风险拦截（高风险动作需玩家批准）</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableRiskApproval>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableRiskApproval.Desc>开启后，达到风险等级阈值的动作会被自动拦截，需玩家批准后才执行。</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.EnableRiskApproval.Desc>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.AutoBlockRiskLevel>自动拦截风险等级阈值：{0}</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.AutoBlockRiskLevel>
    <RimMind.Advisor.Settings.AutoBlockRiskLevel.Desc>达到此风险等级的动作会被自动拦截，需玩家批准后才执行。</RimMind.Advisor.Settings.AutoBlockRiskLevel.Desc>

